This document contains technical specifications and cost estimates based on

information available as of 4 March 2026. The following items are subject to

Change:

Equipment pricing: Valid until quote expiration dates noted

Specifications: Subject to manufacturer updates

Availability: Subject to vendor stock and lead times

Performance figures: Based on manufacturer datasheets under standard conditions

Items marked "TBC" (To Be Confirmed) or "Estimated" require final vendor

confirmation before procurement.

Quote Expiration Dates:

Audiotek QU-20070 (Room 1 Audio): Expires 27 March 2026

Audiotek QU-20071 (Room 2 Audio): Expires 27 March 2026

Goo Systems QU-0932 (Surface Treatment): Expires 3 April 2026

idirnet assumes no liability for changes in vendor pricing or product

specifications after the date of this document.

For questions or clarifications, contact:

Krisjanis Berzins, Technical Lead

Email: kris@idirnet.com

Phone: +353 872275422

